{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3c0023b1a0","title":"第三次声明","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1e3b470713","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":24,"articleId":"3c0023b1a0"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"220cd77e52","name":"“史本三”徐道衡"},{"id":"4887be41ca","name":"华南师范学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a30730dd98","type":"title","text":"第三次声明","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0"},{"id":"598e86ca0a","type":"authors","text":"华南师范学院“史本三”徐道衡","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0"},{"id":"3fa281d886","type":"paragraph","text":"《还我河山》一文昨天已开了辩论会，现在我们再次声明：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0"},{"id":"df66e821af","type":"paragraph","text":"一、我们承认：这样一个涉及到中苏两国关系的问题，采用大字报的形式提出来，从客观影响上看是不好的。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0"},{"id":"fc151b2c11","type":"paragraph","text":"二、我们承认：《还我河山》笼统提出收回领土问题，尽管我们内容上阐述了对苏联要采取谈判方式解决，但也用这标题来对待我们的友邦是错误的。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0"},{"id":"b67f75fa09","type":"paragraph","text":"三、虽然我们要求苏联归还这些领土，但我们并不坚持一定要苏联交还这些领土，如果能对这一问题作合法的解释，可以不交还。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0"},{"id":"6026f4f2a0","type":"paragraph","text":"四、昨天的辩论会并没有解决我们所提出的根本问题，因此我们准备再一次辩论会继续辩论(按：后来没开成)。由于目前我们正在准备考试，所以不再在大字报上争论。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0"},{"id":"52daca9404","type":"paragraph","text":" 《还我河山》作者1957年6月24日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0"},{"id":"e868bb65d6","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：华南师范学院学生会 编辑出版《华南师范学院反右派斗争初战记》，1957年9月。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0"}],"page":{"id":"d5886aee95","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3c0023b1a0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}